com.analog.lyric.dimple.schedulers.scheduleEntry

Class BlockScheduleEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.analog.lyric.dimple.schedulers.scheduleEntry.BlockScheduleEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IScheduleEntry

    public class BlockScheduleEntry
extends java.lang.Object
implements IScheduleEntry
    A schedule entry that contains a collection of nodes to be updated together.

    This class is primarily targeted at the Gibbs solver for block Gibbs updates. For that case, all of the nodes in the collection would be variables.

    0.06
